Invocation Name: fine tune radio
des: Fine Tune Radio is a alternative station in Canada. We are a sister station of Eternity Ready Radio. We play the best christian and family friendly music of the 80s, 90s and 2000s. We are a positive alternative and play best mix of christian and secular music from past and present.
